HEADWORD: Grader
<hw>Grad"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
grades, or that by means of which grading is done or
facilitated.</def></p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <specif>Specifically:</specif> <def>A vehicle used for
levelling earth, esp. one with a plow blade suspended from the center,
used specifically for grading roads.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gradient</ent>⟦br⟧
